			<iframe src=""></iframe>

		</article>

	</div>

</section>

<section id="home-story">

	<div class="container">

		<a class="top" href="#"></a>

		<article id="story">

			<div class="intro">

				<h2>Our Story</h2>
				<h3>How Intercom.fm came to be</h3>

			</div>

			<p>
				Ahh, Southern California.  The land of beautiful people, beautiful weather and...  Wait a minute.  It’s the characters that make this place and this country so amazing.  And now technology has freed up the grasp of authority.  Intercom.fm’s technology is here to kill the radio star and the gatekeepers who traditionally have decided who the next radio star is going to be.  Intercom.fm is a revolution in freedom that puts the power directly in your hands.  Pandora, Spotify, Slacker and others have given the listener authority and we love it.  Intercom.fm takes it one step further and gives everyone the chance to also fully express themselves through creativity.  Go forth with Intercom.fm and be the you you know you can be.  Express, create and inspire here on Intercom.fm.  
			</p>

		</article>

	</div>

</section>

<section id="home-listen">

	<div class="container">

		<a class="top" href="#"></a>

		<article id="listen">

			<div class="intro">

				<h2>Listen</h2>
				<h3>Comedy, Sports, Music Scene, Entertainment, Food Reviews or create your own</h3>

			</div>

			<ul>
				<li>Discover amazing and unique radio shows like nothing you’ve ever heard before.</li>
				<li>You customize, control, and listen to shows in a playlist format.  What you want when you want in our :30 second micro show format.</li>
				<li>Multi-track and sound editing features allow for complete customization of your shows or comment on your favorite shows inside the app.</li>
			</ul>

		</article>

		<article id="listen-screenshot">

			<img src="/content/images/web-explore.png">

		</article>

	</div>

</section>

<section id="home-create">

	<div class="container">

		<a class="top" href="#"></a>

		<article id="create-intro">
		
			<div class="intro">

				<h2>Create</h2>
				<h3>Record, customize, and mix your recordings to create your own audio mix to share</h3>

			</div>

		</article>

		<article class="create-step">

			<h4>Record:</h4>
			<p>Record your voice or other sounds from your phone.</p>
			<img src="/content/images/web-record.png">

		</article>

		<article class="create-step">

			<h4>Customize:</h4>
			<p>Make your sounds perfect in the sound effects area.</p>
			<img src="/content/images/web-customize.png">

		</article>

		<article class="create-step">

			<h4>Mix:</h4>
			<p>Mix your different sounds and tracks together.</p>
			<img src="/content/images/web-mix.png">

		</article>

	</div>

</section>

